snippet.title: Taskmaster
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official Taskmaster YouTube channel. 

Watch Taskmaster episodes from around the globe, as well as best bits, compilations and everything in between. 

Series 12 of Taskmaster starts Thursday 23rd September on Channel 4. 

Emmy Award nominated, and BAFTA and Broadcast Award winning Taskmaster, hosted by Greg Davies as The Taskmaster and his loyal assistant Little Alex Horne, challenges some of the funniest people in the country to use their wit, wile, and wisdom to impress The Taskmaster. Join us in this hyper-competitive and hyper-ridiculous mission to beat The Taskmaster.
